<li><a href="http://www.ImmigrationVoice.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.ImmigrationVoice.org/" rel="nofollow">www.ImmigrationVoice.org</a> Issues facing H-1B holders during the transition to Legal Permanent Residency</li>
<li><a href="http://www.memp.pratt.duke.edu/downloads/americas_new_immigrant_entrepreneurs.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.memp.pratt.duke.edu/downloads/americas_new_immigrant_entrepreneurs.pdf" rel="nofollow">"America's New Immigrant Entrepreneurs"</a> - A Duke University Study</li>
